thread.title_full: BRIEF-TSMC August sales T$67.04 bln, down 3.2 pct y/y | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: TSMC August sales T$67.04 bln, down 3.2 pct y/y
text:
Sept 10 TSMC says:
* August sales T$67.04 billion ($2.06 billion) (July T$80.95 billion, August 2014 T$69.23 billion)
* August sales down 3.2 percent on year
* January-August sales up 23.6 percent on year to T$575.47 billion Source text for Eikon: [ID: bit.ly/1MdcgHK ] ($1 = 32.5750 Taiwan dollars) (Reporting by J.R. Wu)
